name: JayWalker (IronWood)
description:
This was my first ever completed game. This was made on scratch and converted to html.  I just felt like reuploading it here so I did.  Was planning on making a mobile version with more stuff but I lost interest in the project. Original project: https://scratch.mit.edu/projects/304322814/

Avoid the cars!
Get the highest score!
Touch Friendly!

Arrow keys to move

or Swipe up/down/right/left to move on mobile
